print("5. NO NODE TRAPPING (Analysis 5):")$
print("   The apparent m_eff^2 divergence at nodes is an artifact.")$
print("   The actual self-wrapping force vanishes at nodes (F ~ phi_perp).")$
print("   Nodes do not create enhanced trapping potential.")$
print("")$

print("6. EXPONENTIALLY SMALL RADIATION (Analysis 6):")$
print("   A finite soliton ALWAYS radiates, but the rate can be")$
